(103, 2, '2023-01-25 09:50:48', '2023-01-25 08:50:48', '<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\">\r\n\r\nSantorini is a beautiful Greek island known for its stunning scenery and clear blue waters. It\'s a popular destination for tourists, and there are many holiday clubs that offer a variety of activities for visitors to enjoy. One such club is the Santorini Holiday Club.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nThe club offers a wide range of activities for visitors of all ages, from swimming and sunbathing on the island\'s beautiful beaches, to exploring the island\'s rich history and culture. Guests can take guided tours of the island\'s ancient ruins, including the famous Akrotiri excavations, or visit the island\'s many museums and art galleries. The club also offers a range of water sports, such as snorkeling, scuba diving, and windsurfing, as well as hiking and biking tours of the island\'s rugged terrain.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nThe club also has a variety of accommodation options, including hotel rooms, apartments and villas, all of which are equipped with modern amenities and offer breathtaking views of the island. Guests can also enjoy a variety of dining options, from traditional Greek tavernas to international restaurants, as well as a range of bars and cafes.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nThe club also offers a range of entertainment options for guests, including live music, dance performances, and traditional Greek shows. Guests can also enjoy a range of spa and wellness services, including massages, yoga and meditation classes, and beauty treatments.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nOverall, the Santorini Holiday Club offers a wide range of activities, accommodation and entertainment options for visitors to the island, making it the perfect choice for those looking for a fun and memorable holiday experience in Santorini.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Voyage de Noce sur l\'ile de Santorin', 'Une jolie maison troglodyte offrant une magnifique vue sur le coucher du soleil.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nBain à remous privé, à 2 minutes à pied, est disponible du mardi au jeudi et samedi.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'voyage-de-noce-sur-lile-de-santorin', '', '', '2023-01-25 09:51:48', '2023-01-25 08:51:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=103', 0, 'product', '', 0),
